<title>2-bedroom apartment for sale</title>
<description>2-Bedroom Apartment for Sale in Germasogeia Tourist Area

Located in the highly sought-after Germasogeia Tourist Area, this 2-bedroom apartment offers an excellent combination of comfort, convenience, and prime location within walking distance to the sea. The area is well-developed and vibrant, with bakeries, cafés, shops, hair salons, and beauty services all nearby, as well as easy access to public transport and main roads.

This property is an ideal choice both for family living and as a smart investment opportunity.

Property Features:

The apartment includes two spacious bedrooms, each large enough to comfortably accommodate both a bed and a workspace. The separate kitchen is fully equipped with all necessary appliances and also features an additional private balcony.

There is one bathroom with a shower. The living room opens onto a large covered veranda, providing extra living space that can be used as a home office or relaxation area.

Situated on the second floor, the apartment offers a practical and convenient layout.

Additional Advantages:

The building exterior was renovated in 2023, while the apartment itself has undergone cosmetic upgrades. It is equipped with new air conditioning units and modern appliances, making it move-in ready.

This property represents a great opportunity for both residential use and investment in one of Limassol’s most popular locations.

For more information, please contact Manager 4.</description>
